A. Flattened plant in flower; B. Portion of the basal part and rhizome of plant showing flower, fruit and fresh cataphyll; C. A Flower with peduncle; D. Longitudinal section of the flower (pistil removed); E. Scales; F. Flower in top view; G. Flower in bottom view; H. Basal half of the perigone with stamens; I. Pistil in top view; J. Pistil in bottom view; K. Fruit on its peduncle, and seed. Photos A–G and I–K taken from the living plant of the holotype 
